Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Japan's Junior Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First set! Game count: 6-2 for Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However close...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how close the liaison of hearts is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,even if the two travel the same road, \Nstruggling through it hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, one of them will be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a long unseen way still lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, one must walk the rest of the way \Ncompletely by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If such predestination is true for us as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm certainly the one quitting the journey first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What words should I bequeath to her? \NWhat feelings should I confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I best spend the little time I have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I accepted this predestination long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was supposed to be fully prepared for its arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I still keep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,chasing her smile time after time, \Nin occasional blankness of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I discovered Oka Hiromi, and we became traveling companions, 3 years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single moment \Nhas been flooded with thousands of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single glimpse of light \Nhas been a blessing from the eternal sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I thought I would meet \Nthe oncoming parting fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the time for that parting is already imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:30.29,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HFFC32A&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur0.4\c&HF2E7E9&)\c&HFEFDFF&\fnGabriola\fs78\pos(323.42,377.14)}Episode 1 \N\N\N\NThe promise of one and only best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already apparent, isn't it, Jin? \NA new champion is being born as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be a champion, but after you and Madame B. went to university this year, it's a trivial{/ mere} High School Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Had we participated, she'd win regardless." \NSo says the inscription on that frown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You should express your emotions frankly \Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage: Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Game count: 6-2, 6-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set count: 2-0 for Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more, Hiromi! \NHave you seen this morning's sports news?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Women tennis world hope has been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,New champion of Japanese juniors, Oka Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd year at Prefectural Nishi High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Munakata-Oka teacher-student combo is unstoppable!{guess}"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am listless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"The rate of Oka's growth in tennis\Ndeserves a special notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a complete novice \Nwhen Coach Munakata discovered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than 3 years passed \Nsince she first played tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, in addition to Oka's natural predisposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the specialists credit Coach Munakata \Nwith astonishing adaptability."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what they wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost 9 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we go to movies in the afternoon? \NHave an irregular holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,9 o'clock!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to yell, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late to the meeting! \NAt 9 in Madame Butterfly's mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Ryuzaki summoned me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On occasion of All-Japan junior championship \Nconclusion yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis Association Board \Ncame up with a following resolution:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With young players \Nfrom universities and high schools as the core,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we will compose a team of 8 men and 8 women \Nfor a tour to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone present has been selected \Nto represent Nishi High.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tour to America?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Todo, Ozaki and finally, my daughter Reika \Nall have already graduated from Nishi High this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you were enlisted as Munakata's disciples, \Nwho is a coach in charge of this tour's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also meant to strengthen your teamwork, \Nso I want you to assist Munakata in every way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Departure is January 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I have prepared \Na practice schedule for everyone. Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Among others from Kanto region is Horiki Saeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, Midorikawa Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible selection of members!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears, even the Association can become really earnest, \Nwhen it comes to nurturing the youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,America was chosen as the best place \Nto get the taste of genuine power tennis in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, it was Coach Munakata's design all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...For Oka's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take it easy, Chiba. \NNo need to stir it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, I think it's an amazing decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka Hiromi and Munakata Jin - the dream those two \Nenvisioned may soon come true in front of our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach is paving the way \Nfor player to fight with all her might.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Player returns the favor \Nby trusting coach unquestioningly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When Munakata discovered Oka and her dispositions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he trained her not just physically and mentally \Nfor tennis, but also spiritually for their common journey.{I have been looking at this one line for 12 last hours, so fuck off}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"By trusting her partner unquestioningly, \NOka returns the favor..."{can't hear the last word}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Player and coach are just a person and a person \Nat the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and a woman, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, marvelous man and woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up: 6 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Roadwork: 8 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Every 2 kilometers, five 50-meter dashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Swing - 500 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, at 10, come to Nishi High court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day until the plane, \NRyuzaki Reika will be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly? \NMy practice opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a practice, but a real match!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least one match per day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Put up a profound battle, \Nas if the life is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter holidays are for going to mall, \Nnot the sports center!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eve is coming, Christmas is almost here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, say, Hiromi, \Nwhat will you wear for the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Hiromi, we've settled on celebrating your victory \Nwith a grandiose{no idea what that "karetaibu"} party! Didn't you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, maybe that special stadium jumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No hint of charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mickey Mouse jean jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The best of three set match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki's service. Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two aren't joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That receive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen it before. \NWhen did she learn to pull off that sort of hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What takes us a year to master, \Nshe goes through in a course of a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She and coach Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you don't eat, Hiromi?\NIt'll become soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go make a quick call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom to? Where to? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... With life on the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I took one set, but that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What about winning tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about "in a week?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, perhaps I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, the life is not yet lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was busy with Association business today. \NBut tomorrow I'm coming to Nishi High.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, I guess you picked up \Nthat 1000 swings practice again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because Oka also works hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo, hurry up so I could introduce you to Oka. {I want to introduce you to Oka sooner.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,While I still have enough strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Jin. You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko, is that you? \NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Reply quicker next time. \NI'm worried you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, did you really visit hospital \Non the day of appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get to America, \NI won't be able to wake you up every morning like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say nonsense, I'm going there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. You shouldn't exert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, because I track your physical condition \Nby the tone of your voice every morn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, don't come. \NYou, too, need extensive training for the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to strip me of this privilege?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The privilege of being your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have had different mothers, \Nwe may have been brought up separately,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm still your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi High, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you strip me off this privilege, \NI'll disclose it to everyone. The truth about your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor joke. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But jokes aside, I sometimes wonder, \Nwouldn't it be better for you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I give it a thought, \NI can't help worrying ever so much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, this rally has been going like that \Nfor 5 minutes already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither is willing to give up that one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,0-15!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Hold that count!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trivial mistakes, like the one just now, \Nshould not affect this match's count!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In this game, only when any side \Nscores a hard-won ace, add points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Power vs. power, technique vs. technique - \Nin this clash, every point is a feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I forbid you to rely on opponent's {mistakes out of }good or bad luck \Nin finishing this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your trivial mistake in particular
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is caused by a flawed basic technique \Ndue to lack of career, like that of Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For every trivial mistake made, \Nmake a lap around sports ground after the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your service now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, once again, I lost to Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, today I managed to bring it to tie break \Nand lost in a close match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One week later - I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But before we leave for America, \NI'll definitely win. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So for the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,my happiness is boundless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with such an amazing mentor by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know? After every match, Madame Butterfly \Nalso does laps around the sports ground along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For the number of her mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do my best, tomorrow too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone! \NListen closely starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishi High tennis club, \Nalong with the alumni association,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,will piggyback on tonight's Christmas party \Nto get festive on two occasions at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First being the birth of All-Japan's juniors \Nnew champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka Hiromi's flight into the world!{/ The victory party for Oka Hiromi.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the second one is \Nthis time's tour to America members selection
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,final approval!{purely guessing, this line is already hard enough to tie up with previous ones}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, let me introduce those members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo Takayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Although still university's 1st year, swift enough \Nto already be Kanto university students champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You may know him \Nas Nishi High's male team ex-captain{ until this year}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Embarrassed himself {/ Only achievement this year is bringing shame on himself}\Nby being #2 among Kanto students this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, he promised to break Todo's leg \Nto emerge as the ultimate winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki Reika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Nishi High student, \Nheld a record of 143 consecutive victories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, as a Saint Maria Women's College student, \Nkeeps mounting that record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With this superb play,\Nshe truly is {\i1}Madame Butterfly{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Collateral new star, \NOka Hiromi. Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to have your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Oka! V-sign, V-sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,V...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't do, more expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, I'll also withdraw my part-time savings \Nto follow everyone to America shortly after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Nishi High's journalism club old boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for those supposed to carry Japan's tennis \Non their shoulders from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,whichever country life hurls them in, \NI want to document it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way. Hiromi, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot too. \NJingle Bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How sumptuous! \NI even get 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this one's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How mystifying. \NIf not me, then a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like a wallet? Mystifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, who, who??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't bother to come tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the club sent him official invitation! \NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also his adorable disciple's victory party!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Munakata! That's haughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A day off from practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave us a furlough just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversational English.\NI thought I should do at least that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From under kotatsu, succumbing to winter{/ Christmas} gluttony{I hear "winter ME eating" but I couldn't find that construction in a dictionary} \Nwith gaufre{sounds like "gofu kara" but I don't know what else a gofu may be and why is anything coming out of it}, rice crackers and shortcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice to meet you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a long time, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have some guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Jin's ancient friend came to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll come back another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, we're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I introduce: Nishi High's Oka Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... You can call me just Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for popping in unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I will have my leave soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Name's Katsura. Katsura Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monk?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a real monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Coach Munakata's bosom friend \Nended up being a devoted head-shaven monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He made me drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Made you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit. \NWe drank while observing the snowfall.{Japanese custom similar to that of watching sakura, dunno how to wrap it up properly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,First time meeting a monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they're called monks, \Nunderneath the bare skull, it's but an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they also usually drink \Njust a bit too much sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time ever I saw coach Munakata \Nlaughing so blissfully while telling stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughing? Our coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Guffawing at the top of his lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to see her, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you bet it all on, \Nthe hidden gem you entrust to me fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By exchanging letters with you, \NI thought I'd find out everything I need to know about Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But seeing her in person still was a shock. \NWhat an unthinkable kind of player.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But more than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,fortunate and terrifying at the same time \Nis that she's still clueless about the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But she'll find out now, one way or another.\NIt'll become complicated from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go to sleep? \NIt's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's fine. \NI can get my futon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't raise voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How many weeks left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At least... At least, give me just enough time \Nto send them off undisturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo, do it for me. \NTake care of it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin, I devoted these last 5 years fully \Nto keeping that one promise to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do everything in my power regardless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're trying to pull off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a... It's a challenge \Nthat would take a miracle to overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it. I know it all, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard, coach Munakata \Ngot hospitalized last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:16.33,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Saka no tochuu de hitori furi muku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,While climbing up the hill, one turns around and looks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though there was not a soul in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:23.65,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Dare mo inai no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:32.15,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Hidamari no naka nayami mo shirazu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sunny spot, blissfully oblivious of worries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we spent days when you were still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:41.17,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ikiteita ano hi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it only when one loses something,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:49.35,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee hito wa itsumo nani ka nakushita toki ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:57.66,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ari no mama no jibun ni kidzuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets to perceive what was actually going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder if you can hear me \Neven while you're not here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:05.67,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee ima wa inai anata kikoeru kashira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a promise to carry on living my own way, \Ntherefore you must also, even if for an eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:16.79,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Watashi rashiku ikite yuku to yakusoku suru kara anata wa itsumade mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:20.35,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Miteite ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep looking after me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:24.26,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Tooku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From your far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:31.72,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,6000)}Miteite ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,6000)}Keep looking after me
