Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aikawa Maki, Hiromi's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That Demon Coach Munakata got hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What will become of Hiromi, \Nwho cares so much for Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as she's about to embark on a tour to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Coach cares about Hiromi at least a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, admittedly, this Coach's hospitalization \Nis kinda worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode:\NOka, aim for the ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:23:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
